SUMMER 2024 HOURS
Lakewood Country Club is excited to announce that we will be OPEN all Summer 2024! We look forward to being able to provide you a place to get your rounds in this Summer! We look forward to seeing you out on the course soon! Tee Times will be available from 7:30 AM to 11:30 AM. Book your next tee time today!
